title: Ondekoza - Legend 1994
description:
The third album from this famous Japanese group, released on the Nektar label, is just amazing. Powerful music with extrem low bass and big dynamic sound, these nine guys and one women makes music that you not only hear, but also feel, if your system can handle it. Because let it be a warning, some tracks are extremly dynamic and have very, very low bass (if you look at the drums they play on, drums that are bigger than a whole drum-set, you understand they will go deep) and they could hurt your system if its not up to snuff. So please play the tunes at low volume first and if you have a great system with a good low end, just enjoy the powerful and extremly well-recorded music. 

The music mainly consist of drums and fue.
